high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the wall and turn right again to face the green bin next to the counter.
Pick up the potato out of the green bin.
Turn around and walk up to the white table, then hang a left and walk up to the microwave.
Heat up the potato in the microwave for a couple seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Put the heated potato inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward, hang a right to the garbage can at the end of the counter.
Pick up the potato that is in the garbage can.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the microwave across the room.
Put the potato inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the potato when it is done cooking.
Turn right and go to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in the fridge.
